                        <interp inst="t18770305-name-230" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE LOCKYER</persName>
                  </hi>. I was present when the prisoner was convicted at this Court, in 1869 he was sentenced to
seven years' penal servitude; he pleaded guilty to the offence, but not to a previous conviction charged against him.</p>
